hadith-eng:
Allah's Messenger (ﷺ) said: The cattle (sheep, cows, camels, etc.) suffering
     from a disease should not be mixed up with healthy cattle, (or said: 
     "Do not put a patient with a healthy person ). " (as a precaution).

